window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>You can listen to this family-friendly story for free on your device with the Audible Stories Skill. Just say “Alexa, read me a nighttime story,” or “Alexa, read me a story” to hear more free genres.</b></p> <p>Gingerella is an undecorated gingerbread girl who, neglected by the royal baker, fears she will not be allowed to the Gingerbread Fair. Running away to the forest, she encounters a woodsman with a secret passion...for baking.</p> <p>A mashup of <i>Cinderella</i> and <i>The Gingerbread Man</i>, this funny and fast-paced fairytale features a medieval baking contest, a ravenous queen and a ginger-bottomed prince!</p>"; 
